I move to amend House Bill No. 4199 as follows:
1. On Page 2, Lines 9 and 10, by deleting after the word “income” on Line 9 and before the
word “and” on Line 10, all language and inserting the words “does not exceed the state’s median
household income, according to the most recent available data from the United States Census
Bureau,”; and
2. On Page 3, Line 1, by inserting after the word “shall” and before the word “report”, the
word “electronically”.
